{"tid":1534401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［經濟求續］文宣派發計劃","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T09:56:37.000Z","uid":81231,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"246f50ef6dd77194925203f7db46d6d98c821e6b","tid":1534401,"uid":81231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"有個諗法，好多人因為發夢，返唔到part time, 特別係星期六，日。 又有和理非，有錢想課就唔知課去邊。<br />\n<br />\n我決定搞個文宣派發計劃，大家出錢出力，另類part time。<br />\n<br />\n暫時構思：<br />\n求職者可當區工作，工資以派發份數計，印刷另計，工時亦不受限制。牆紙個啲，可以係5蚊一份，單頁文宣2蚊一份，又有工返，又維持到生活，又推動到運動。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣，大家俾啲意見，幾日內成事。"},{"pid":"46f8f95cb606ae186ce7405ba006c8dd8ece0708","tid":1534401,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad384d0245709a5de005365efc50fafe24a37185","tid":1534401,"uid":81231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:47:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ee02d5a9ce514dad7dc268caf581c99f9240c503","tid":1534401,"uid":81231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:47:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a817ae29b913f678f3000ebf3c9360a3ae4c115e","tid":1534401,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:48:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"325591107a7ebf1f1e408855148741358da208bd","tid":1534401,"uid":81231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:48:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"82cb28d404b3ea4ec0dc0857b8c1c9b8fe0d7152","tid":1534401,"uid":81231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:48:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7fc383715ea8ca9e4980daf00b392d01193927b2","tid":1534401,"uid":92385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0